minim http://code.compartmental.net/tools/minim/

To use:
* delete <processing>/modes/java/libraries/minim/ (older version)
* unzip downloaded minim to <sketchbook>/libraries/

Wacky pulseaudio madness:
* find /usr/lib/jvm -name pulse-java.jar
* copy to <processing>/java/lib/ext/
* find /usr/lib/jvm -name libpulse-java.so
* copy to <processing>/java/lib/i386/
https://forum.processing.org/topic/why-can-t-i-play-more-than-one-audiosample

